short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The mythical barber from Atlanta will be answering your questions.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the world of Humpfate, a fun and mysterious fortune-teller game where your destiny is decided with a simple yes or no answer! Inspired by the enigmatic style of Brandon Currington, Humpfate brings a touch of mystique and unpredictability to your daily life. Simply type your question, and let the fortune teller reveal your fate. Will it be a "yes" or a "no"? Only Humpfate knows!
